## map_builder.lsl — deliver board_mover to root tile

In `run_time_permissions`, after the linking loop and before `llBreakLink(1)`:

```lsl
// Give board_mover to tile (0,0) — it will become root after llBreakLink(1).
// Requires "board_mover" script to be in the builder prim's inventory.
if (llGetInventoryType("board_mover") != INVENTORY_NONE)
    llGiveInventory(llList2Key(gTileKeys, 0), "board_mover");

llBreakLink(1);
llOwnerSay("[BLD] Board linked! Add to controller inventory.");
llDie();
```

**Inventory requirement:** The user must place `board_mover.lsl` (compiled) in the **MapBuilder** prim before building. The builder delivers it automatically to the right tile.

